b1 exd4 {This does not work.} 22. Rxb4 dxc3 23. Rxb7 {The point.} Qc8 24. Qxd8+ Qxd8 25. Ra8 Nfd7 26. Rxd7 Qb6 27. Rd1 {We ended up in a technical endgame, where the c3 pawn is weak and White has a great chance of getting the full point.} *

