. Nd2 {This idea could be a new path in this line.} (16. a5 $5 {was played by Jeffery. I do not like it as much, and that's why I keep it as a clickable only.} Qe8 17. Qb3 Bd5 18. Bc4 Nc6 19. Nxc6 Bxc6 {Here, I would recommend a slight improvement over Jeffery's move.} 20. Bd4 $5 {and maybe White has some slight pressure here, but of course, with few accurate moves, Black should be able to neutralize it. Bxf6 gxf6= was just equal in Xiong-Dominguez, 2021.}) 16... Nc6 17. Nc4 Bc5 18. Nb3 {And the bishop is chased around. White is pressing.} *

