..} 26. h4 {Bb7 h5 Bxd5+ Kh2} Qxg1+ 27. Kxg1 Be6 28. Qf6 h6 29. Qxh6 dxc4 {or Rxg6+ hxg6 Kg1 Bb7 d6 Rd8} 30. Qf4 Bd5 31. Qe5 Be6 32. Kf1 {c4 Ke2} b5 {Qxb5 c3= and eventually Black should make a draw by setting up a fortress once the d6 -pawn falls.}) *

