k has issues with the king.}) (18. Qb6 {intending ... Qb4 is the safest continuation for Black. ( Qe7 is the same) O-O-O Qb4 Bxg7} Rg8 19. b3 {Qxc3+ Bxc3} Nc5 $1 {intending ... Ne4 and Black should be able eventually to equalize.} 20. h5 $5 {controls the g6 -square and threatens Bf6 .} Ne4 21. Bxe4 fxe4 22. Bf6 {Rg4!= and ... Rf4 .}) *

