s too strong and had to be dealt with sooner or later.} 15. Bxf5 Nc4 {Black gave away the pair of bishops but simplified the position and obtained a great knight on c4 . But I don't think Black equalized:} 16. Bd3 Re8 17. a4 {Again, I will stand firmly for White here as the pair of bishops should be meaningful in the long run.} *

