ive. We have some choice, but I like the following the most.} 18. axb4 Bxd2 (18... axb4 19. Bxb4) 19. Nxd2 {Taking with the queen and regaining the pawn was possible too, but I feel like it is more important to bring the knight to c4 from where it can go even to d6 !} axb4 20. Nc4 {White has very good compensation.} *

