e advancing central pawns, or going for h4 - h5 !? With perfect play, perhaps Black can be OK here, but it looks better for White.} (18. f4 $5 {is another option.}) 18... Qc7 19. f4 ({With an advantage for White. Nf6} 19. Bf6 $5 gxf6 20. h4 {or Rdd1} Rad8 {Bf3⩲}) *

