Rxa6 Rxh2} (33... Rf2 34. Bg6+ {Ke7 f5⩲}) 34. Be4 {Rh4 Re6+ With f5 next. Black still needs to make a draw here, even though the engine shows 0.1-0.2 evaluations.}) *

