 Qd3 {This is a good alternative which also pushes Black to the limit.} Ne4 {White can play simply now.} 15. Bd2 Nxc3 (15... Nxd2 16. Nxd2 {the b7 -pawn is attacked.}) 16. Qxc3 b6 17. Rfc1 {With an advantage.} *

