en - in the event of opening the c-file White will be ready for it. Additionally, there is some pressure on the f5 -pawn, making it not possible to recapture it with the e-pawn!} Ne4 11. e3 Qe7 (11... g5 12. b4 g4 13. Ne1 {with Nd3 next.}) 12. Ne2 {Going for the knight's maneuver.} b6 (12... g5 13. Rfc1) 13. Qa4 Bb7 14. cxd5 exd5 (14... cxd5 15. Rfc1) 15. h4 {White is clearly better.} *

